{
  "stem": "21527.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She became a very close friend, and we spent time with her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She lived with us after the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she was-- we actually brought her out here, and she lived here for many years before she died.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the man whom she married after the war was an orderly, medical orderly in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she was the nurse.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Paula.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Morris.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were-- there were some other people in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were people here still in Melbourne that we were in camps with.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was just-- the, the bond was just fantastic because we'd been through so much together that there was a sort of a lasting bond between us.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My uncle was head of the hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was also sort of an unofficial leader of the ghetto because the real leader was so corrupt.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My uncle was so good and so helpful that the people came to him not only for medical advice, but just for moral support, I think, for a kind word, which he was always able to give to everybody.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that extended after the liberation as well because people were just so alone.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "At least we were still a family unit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "People were just so alone, so they came just for a kind word.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just to keep on living.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not to give in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think just hope that one day it would be over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We, we really didn't know, not just from one day to another, but from one minute to another.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Could have been shot, could get some terrible illness, could just die.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- it was pretty horrible, very frightening, pretty horrible.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They knew-- well, actually, we knew at what stage America entered the war.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
